						<div class="postbody">O.k., to make sure I didn't misunderstand you, let's put this together:<br /><br />Question 1:<br />In &quot;Super Mario Bros. 3&quot;, do you think that small Mario has regular size while Super Mario is a giant?<br />Or do you think that small Mario is a dwarf while Super Mario has regular size?<br /><br />Question 2:<br />In &quot;Super Mario Bros. 3&quot;, do you think that Princess Toadstool and Toad have regular size or are they giants?<br /><br />(With regular size I'm not talking about &quot;default&quot; size. Which one is the default is not important here. I'm talking about the actual absolute values. Regular size would be something like 1.55 m (or maybe 1.30 for Toad) to 2.10 m. Giant would mean 3 m and dwarf means 70 cm.)</div>

					
